(3) Delegation of powers to various functionaries for taking decision on the transfer or acquisition of the loans;
(4) Stated objectives for acquiring stressed assets;
(5) Risk premium to be applied for the purpose of paragraph 73, which requires that for acquired stressed loans, if the net present value of estimated cash flows is less than the consideration paid, provisions shall be maintained for the difference, using a discount factor that includes a risk premium determined by this policy; etc.

